title: Elegant Appetizers
description: A new way to look at Formal Entertaining!  Entertaining expert and chef Andrea Correale provides wonderful ideas and recipes for elegant appetizers.  The products featured are the Eternal Gold Stemware and the Gilded Tapestry Dinnerware from Lenox.  These items can be found at Lenox.com!
